      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The high-revving naturally aspirated powerplant benefits from a recent double-VANOS overhaul and valve adjustment. Mechanically sound, the chassis maintains its structural integrity with reinforced subframe mounts. Performance is anchored by a factory limited-slip differential and M-tuned suspension, offering exceptional lateral grip and communicative steering feedback. Finished in Carbon Black, the exterior shows honest wear consistent with its era, while the interior retains its driver-focused ergonomics. A turn-key enthusiast machine optimized for peak longitudinal and transverse dynamics.",
